## 📖 Overview

### Semester 1

* 🤖 Artificial Intelligence
* 🗄️ Database Programming
* 🏢 Enterprise Systems Design and Modelling
* 🇫🇷 French Language
* 🔧 Instrumentation & Measurement
* 🗣️ Professional Communication Skills 2

### Semester 2

* 📱 Application Development
* 📊 Business Intelligence
* 💼 Entrepreneurship and Innovation
* 🚀 High Performance Data Processing
* 📚 Special Topic in Data Engineering

Year 3 focused on both technical and professional development. The courses provided exposure to Artificial Intelligence, Database Systems, Enterprise Architecture, Business Intelligence, Big Data Processing, Mobile Application Development, Entrepreneurship, and Data Engineering. In addition, communication and language courses helped strengthen presentation, teamwork, negotiation, and interpersonal skills, creating a balanced learning experience that prepared me for industry projects and future career opportunities.

